</taxonomicName>
- CUSHMAN, p. 67, pl. 23, figs. 24-26.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6336F3FFFFFFBEFF3D9F996813796F" blockId="18.[151,757,904,1039]" pageId="18" pageNumber="32">
